OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with a band
OL,6,Fof rain crossing from the west,
OL,7,Fperhaps with the odd heavier burst.
OL,8,FThis clearing the east by mid-
OL,9,Fafternoon, leaving some sunshine and
OL,10,Fisolated showers. Mostly dry by
OL,11,Fevening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA breezy night with all areas
OL,14,Fexpected to remain dry with some long
OL,15,Fclear spells likely across the region.
OL,16,FFeeling chilly by end of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
