OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSunshine for Sunday morning
OL,6,Fthen afternoon showers likely, these
OL,7,Fpotentially heavy. A windy day with
OL,8,Ftemperatures mostly around average,
OL,9,Fbut overnight ground frost is possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FSunshine and showers for Monday, with
OL,13,Fheavy downpours by afternoon. Drier by
OL,14,Fevening. Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,15,Fcloudier with increasing chance of
OL,16,Fshowers. Breezy, but milder with
OL,17,Fslightly above average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
